OL,3,C'We're very scared': Mountain
OL,4,Ccommunities in Pakistan fear for
OL,5,Cfuture as glaciers melt
OL,7,FIt took us 21 hours to reach Passu
OL,8,Ffrom Islamabad. Our flight up to the
OL,9,Fnearest city of Gilgit was cancelled
OL,10,Fso we had to drive the whole way
OL,11,Finstead.
OL,13,FWe left at night and by dawn we were
OL,14,Fentering the foothills of the
OL,15,FKarakorum Mountain range. The sun
OL,16,Fslowly revealed one of the most
OL,17,Fstunning landscapes and the highest
OL,18,Fpeaks I've ever seen.
